Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:15.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:36.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:44.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:52.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:02:00.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:08.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:14.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的愿望  摇曳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:15.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让飞雪滑过脸颊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}挥之不去的后悔  紧系过去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北风的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一触即散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:36.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夹杂着寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:44.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越过了眼中的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:52.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在想给你的旋律  遥指着初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:02:00.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼凑出的未来  手指间露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:08.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要实现在此看见的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:14.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}约定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在涟漪的水面深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映着蔚蓝的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来又将飘零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季节长存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们编织命运之丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却从来都不曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这丝线将通向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(仅仅伫立于此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每当我与他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灵感乍现时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已经隐约察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终会有结束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终有渐渐打开之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好时光关入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不过我会在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}写下一句「我没事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现我的愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  诺艾尔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:28.59,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(32,270)}「两人的约定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋两个够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半熟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}关于来年飞碟应对费的上涨  预算委员会今早…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还穿着这身不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被爸爸这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶得及的话倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶得及…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是开学典礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  现在才八月份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比东京要早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小学时是一样的  我以为你知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么久的事情我怎么会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦把面包烤上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古宫乃乃香  还请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容再多一些不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋都已经全熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说「随你」的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这个时间了  因为爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到迷路的孩子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你不是观光客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是刚刚搬过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经知道分到哪个班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少有人在这个小镇上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在一个班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古宫乃乃香  还请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  大家要成为好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宫同学  你的座位在第二列的最后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢碰到  绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然听见了  至少给个回应什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我们在湖边见过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道为什么你说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宫同学  一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我乃乃香就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也叫我小春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家住在湖边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确说是在山那边  离湖还是有点距离的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有今天早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  你是搬到雾弥湖町来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  水坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么想的  我想问个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢还是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只飞碟！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦  要两杯姜汁汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香也喝这个可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…刚才说到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续那个话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊  这很重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要激动  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不知道  七年前可是引起了很大的轰动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻上有播  我还有些印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那个时候我正好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是当事者的话  就一定有不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟忽然降临  就那样架在湖上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是居然谁都没有放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  饮料来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那个飞碟  麻烦才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  把我的也喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并没有打扰到小镇上的人们  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年了  看起来只是漫不经心地浮在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道背地里在干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇的安全一天天被威胁着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁为时未晚  不做些什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得小镇本身就代表着安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟和烦恼中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香选择哪一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是烦恼中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了恢复小镇的和平而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(320,50,320,65)\bord0\1c000000\fs30\t(\fs27)}反对飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起恢复小镇的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  乃乃香也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要叫名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大声喊出来  是传达不出去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  这样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把飞碟从小镇赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的小镇不需要飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱赶之计  刻不容缓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要持续到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到飞碟消失为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以把它驱赶出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢  两位顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是…必要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是道歉为好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我们又没有…做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  好好把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春的脾气我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你能一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是顺势跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就开始下一项作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一项？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,26)\1cE7E7E7\3c2F2F2F\fs18\frz5.5\fscx95}飞碟应对科
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于飞碟的事  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请先填一下这张表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想直接和飞碟的负责人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里管事的人给我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接和管事的人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和管事的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把管事的人叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你在窗口叫  管事的人也不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座岛  以前是可以坐游轮过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是后来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为危险就禁止进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事  果然很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要把我们的小镇夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要生柚季的气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心情我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这样就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和凑太没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也和你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你不要给别人惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是些毫无意义的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是飞碟和那个人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诉诸武力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向岛进发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这绝对不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做到这种程度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包拿上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生我的气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么想把飞碟赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为七年前飞碟出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而让一样东西改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在也无法恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有烟花从湖面升起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然规模不是那么壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但水面倒映出的烟花却非常美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在已经不会再放了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是会飞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射这枚火箭试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全飞不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起把飞碟赶出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不许做危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须再找些人来帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好遵守和妈妈的约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好好遵守了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的好女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不起精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么困扰的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔能帮上忙的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔能来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔要怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把飞碟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小镇的上空赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香讨厌飞碟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想为朋友做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意再给我一点时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就有三个人了
